torage先"},{"pid":"bbc583540dbac0325f54660c34254d761e1d9e4f","tid":60692,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱裝咗1000M寬頻，師傅用佢部notebook測速下載有900mbps，但我插自己部電腦得400幾mbps，線材好似全部係cat5<br />\n<br />\n電腦: MSI B150m gaming內置lan card<br />\nRouter: ASUS AC58u<br />\n<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點先行到個正常速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1) 放棄wifi ，一定要用全LAN,   PC &lt;==&gt; Router &lt;==&gt; Modem 全Cat 6 Patch cable連住<br />\nWifi = 必定大打折扣<br />\n<br />\n2) PC不得使用任何Firewall以免network speed減<br />\n<br />\n3) <a href=\"http://用Speedtest.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%94%A8Speedtest.com&d=kSFyrtAl1ZjcKOb9X29sHXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=33382806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">用Speedtest.com</a>個D試<br />\n<br />\n4) 測試時唔好開多餘software，最好岩岩開機個陣就試<br />\n<br />\n試下個下載去唔去到800~900 Mbps<br />\n上載應該都有700~800 Mbps"},{"pid":"da690cf68d2a147327dc7721bc4b1df25f96dafb","tid":60692,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"400同1000有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20aaa50567f9e06716fe09ca1c069098900882a","tid":60692,"uid":44917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>modem連router同router連電腦<br />\n2條都要cat6<br />\n<br />\n利申試過 已解決</blockquote><br />\n點解個師傅用部好舊嘅thinkpad，直插同經過router插都行到900m，但我部desktop又唔得，明明兩條線都冇換過"},{"pid":"711d1247064762032302e7ff7296447ba8c29859","tid":60692,"uid":44917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主做乜storage先</blockquote><br />\n咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f947d3316c420534fb03a817924ce15c1db7d0d0","tid":60692,"uid":44917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12